{/* Full Stack Web Application */}

🚀 Enterprise Credential Management Platform

VelocityCreds — A revolutionary blockchain-powered credential verification system that transforms how organizations issue and verify digital credentials. Built during an intensive 4-month development sprint with{' '} Velocity Network Foundation {' '} partners, this platform now serves as the backbone for credential verification across multiple industries.

The challenge: Create a secure, scalable solution that bridges traditional credentialing with cutting-edge blockchain technology while maintaining seamless user experience.

  • ⚡ Cloud-Native Architecture: Deployed via containerized Docker infrastructure on DigitalOcean with auto-scaling capabilities
  • 🎨 Modern Frontend: Built with React.js and Material UI for responsive, intuitive user interactions
  • 🔧 Robust Backend: Express.js API with MongoDB for high-performance data management and real-time processing
  • 🔐 Blockchain Integration: Secure credential verification using Velocity Network's decentralized infrastructure

Live Application:{' '} velocitycreds.com {' '} — Experience the future of credential verification

{/* Published Game Development */}

🎮 Viral Physics-Based Platformer

Grippy Yellow Ball — What started as a creative experiment became a global phenomenon! This meticulously crafted physics-based platformer has captured the hearts of over 40,000+ players worldwide across multiple gaming platforms.

The journey: From concept to publication, this project showcased the complete game development lifecycle — ideation, prototyping, extensive playtesting, polish, and multi-platform distribution.

🏆 Key Achievements:

  • 🌍 Global Reach: 40,000+ active players across{' '} GX.games {' '} and other major platforms
  • ⚡ Advanced Physics: Custom-built physics engine optimized for fluid, responsive gameplay
  • 🎯 User-Centric Design: Iterative development based on extensive community feedback and testing
  • 📱 Cross-Platform Ready: Optimized for web, mobile, and desktop environments

Play it now: Experience the addictive gameplay that hooked thousands of players!
